---


<section class="hero" id="inicio">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <div class="hero-text">
                <h1>Soluciones tecnológicas para la Administración Pública</h1>
                <p>Más de 20 años desarrollando software especializado para la Administración Pública. Un servicio de atención al cliente personalizado que marca la diferencia.</p>
                <a href="#contacto" class="btn">Solicitar información</a>
                <a href="#productos" class="btn btn-outline">Ver soluciones</a>
            </div>
            <div class="hero-image">
                <img src="escudo_por_defecto.png" alt="Administración Pública Digital">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>


<style>
  
.hero {
    background: var(--gradient-dark);
    color: white;
    padding: 220px 0 150px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
}

.hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background-image: 
        linear-gradient(rgba(0, 69, 255, 0.05) 1px, transparent 1px),
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0, 69, 255, 0.05) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 30px 30px;
    animation: grid-animation 15s linear infinite;
}

.hero-content {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
}

.hero-text {
    flex: 1;
    max-width: 600px;
    position: relative;
}

.hero h1 {
    font-size: 56px;
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 25px;
    position: relative;
    text-shadow: 0 5px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(30px);
    animation: fadeUp 1s cubic-bezier(0.19, 1, 0.22, 1) 0.5s forwards;
}

.hero p {
    font-size: 18px;
    margin-bottom: 35px;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(30px);
    animation: fadeUp 1s cubic-bezier(0.19, 1, 0.22, 1) 0.7s forwards;
    text-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
}

.hero .btn {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(30px);
    animation: fadeUp 1s cubic-bezier(0.19, 1, 0.22, 1) 0.9s forwards;
    margin-right: 15px;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
}

.hero-image {
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: flex-end;
    margin-left: 80px;
    position: relative;
    perspective: 1000px;
}

.hero-image img {
    filter: brightness(0) invert(1);
    max-width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-lg);
    box-shadow: 0 30px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    transform: translateZ(0);
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeIn 1s ease 1.2s forwards;
}
</style>